This delicious ramen shop is run by a friendly, cheerful manager and his fun-loving coworkers.
As the main target is overseas customers, much of the menu is in English, but Japanese customers won't have any problems.
This time I had the chicken paitan ramen, which was delicious with a deep flavorful soup that clung to the noodles just right. The drink menu also has a selection of drinks to go with the ramen. I had a Coke.
Perhaps because the target customer is overseas, the prices are a little on the higher side, but the food is well worth it.
Please do stop by.
